{"tid":2383724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"愛的家(Family Mask)口罩菌落超標　2人涉安全條例被捕","createTime":"2021-01-28T05:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T06:12:31.000Z","uid":30040,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca970a5fd248f08599a91b933d4ed361b31b9b9","tid":2383724,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"海關化驗市面售賣的口罩，其中在佐敦購買的一款本港品牌「愛的家」(Family Mask)彩色口罩，細菌菌落總數超出上限12.5倍。生產商董事及化妝品零售店經理，涉嫌違反《消費品安全條例》被捕。<br />\n<br />\n海關消費品安全課總貿易管制主任陳國雄表示，已在市面檢獲約1500個同款的「季節限定」口罩，市值約4500元，相信流入市面的數量不多，並已檢獲市面全部存貨。海關指，涉案口罩在九龍區的無塵間廠房生產，主要供應本地市場，以5個一袋發售，包裝上有標明「ASTM LEVEL 3」等防護效能。海關化驗同一品牌其他彩色口罩，暫未發現有問題，會繼續調查口罩細菌菌落超標的原因，包括原材料是否有問題。<br />\n<br />\n「愛的家」是在疫情初期，由香港旅遊促進會創會會長鍾偉棠，以及他的女兒鍾銘思牽頭成立，首批盒裝口罩在去年4月初推出市面。"},{"pid":"256e663302384301d8c9333be69426de8bc40dd8","tid":2383724,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"藍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84cc79361c1fa6875b1c36e2cf3b9ca266a36d2","tid":2383724,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"鬥藍？"},{"pid":"554325f345a3c044975311668217a646c3c66832","tid":2383724,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"無封利是？"},{"pid":"5dbd699e8d5c6e39b5e4aedae8692888dc18f0fb","tid":2383724,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"係咪政協黎？"},{"pid":"c317d9000f5512cf91f6ac46d9aa1861685d2f45","tid":2383724,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55b0cb94f35c58ab91dcb7cfcef77e8258bead0","tid":2383724,"uid":210253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:12:31.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<br />\n但唔驚，仲有栗正屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}